text.tspan: Graph Drawing Contest 2021 · Ammer David · Korpitsch Thorsten · Pointner Simon
Movie order is optimized with a meta heuristic approach, in detail simulated annealing. The cost is defined as the divergence of movies,
of the same director, from their centroid. This will optimally result in a minimum number of crossings between movies directed
by the same director. The original graph is rendered with D3, while further adjustments are performed using Inkscape.
Images of movies are accessed from IMDB.
The movie data is provided by the 29th
